Author: TiredMama90
Text: I had a guy who I rarely saw (my mums best friends ex) say to me once “you look good,really really good!”.  He’s someone that NEVER talks to anyone let alone gives compliments!

Author: noonelovesacowgirl
Text: It's a good feeling!   Someone I hadn't seen an couple months (which happened to be mostly a restrictive phase) once told me "you've shrunk!" with complete surprise. I took an embarrassingly long time to understand. My first reply was something dumb like "um I don't think I got shorter..."
